-- CANADA RESEARCH ROUNDUP-Bank Of Montreal, Rubicon Minerals
-- 
-- Thu May 29, 2014 03:03AM EDT
-- None



May 29 (Reuters) - Securities analysts revised their ratings and price targets on several Canadian companies, including Bank Of Montreal and Rubicon Minerals, on Thursday.

HIGHLIGHTS * Bank Of Montreal <BMO.TO>: Canaccord Genuity, CIBC, National Bank Financial raise target * Rubicon Minerals <RMX.TO>: Canaccord Genuity starts with speculative buy ratingFollowing is a summary of research actions on Canadian companies reported by Reuters on Thursday. Stock entries are in alphabetical order. * Bank Of Montreal <BMO.TO>: Canaccord Genuity raises target price to C$79 from C$78; hold * Bank Of Montreal <BMO.TO>: CIBC raises target price to C$81 from C$79; sector performer  * Bank Of Montreal <BMO.TO>: National Bank Financial raises target price to C$81 from C$79 * Canacol Energy <CNE.TO>: Canaccord Genuity raises target price to C$12 from C$9.25; buy  * National Bank Of Canada <NA.TO>: CIBC raises target to C$49 from C$48;sectorunderperformer * Rubicon Minerals <RMX.TO>: Canaccord Genuity starts with target price C$1.60  * Rubicon Minerals <RMX.TO>: Canaccord Genuity starts with speculative buy rating